Name: Orchestration Movement III
AttributesDescription: Phrolova composed this melody upon the founding of the Fabricatorium. She blended the music of her past into it, wishing that those dear and near to her might one day play it in the real world.
BgDescription: Incomplete sheet music, part of the core melody regulating the Fabricatorium of the Deep.
